'''Tassast''' deg [[Tasnafsit|tesnimant]] d afray (aḥulfu) s [[atmelli|utmelli]] d wadad d tuẓẓma. Dɣa [[Asken|isekna]] n tassast mgaraden neɣ ugten seg s ufray s temzalt (ṛṛwaḥ) n tezmert, afray s [[aneẓmi|uneẓmi]], antuter amatu, turnant, [[tunɣayt]], [[Tawarrẓa (tasnimant)|Tawarrẓa]], alluy d uɣelluy n [[adad n yidammen|wadad n yidammen]], [[arfey]], [[Anfa]], imrayen deg [[anagraw amaẓẓad|unagraw amaẓẓad]], yakk d [[iẓmi|yiẓmi]] yakked d isekna n [[tarda]] ɣer tullas. Yerna tassast tezmer ad teglu i wemdan s wuguren niden meqqren am wuguren n [[ul|wul]] neɣ s yifrayen ur nelhi ara ɣef yiman-is. 

Tudert n wemdan d tin i d-issuturen drus n tassast, acku anecta d ayen yelhan i tezmert. Anda i tettallel deg usgirrez n tmellit tanaddalt, akken i tga d amgi aseraɣ i ttaǧǧan amdan ad [[assezgi|yessezgi w ad yennam]] tawennaṭ-is.

